          "URL": "https://www.thetvdb.com/series/one-week-friends/episodes/4845954",
          "TitleEnglish": "Last Day With Friends",
          "SummaryEnglish": "The four friends get together on the last day of Summer break to finish up assignments Yuki learns about how much of a difference he's made in Kaori's life.",
